ANTIPHON
-
~Failed attempts at self-expression
~No regrets and no impression
~Is it really mightier than the sword
~-
~All my takes are hot and all mine
~Givens changing every season
~Reason always feeling far too cold
~-
~Meant to be seen as a whole
~Under stares singing coal
~Right until the rain puts out the flame
~-
~Only one to read is one to write
~And only two times in his life
~Before the time to lie
~And before the time to die
